prompt_template:
Create a {ASPECT_RATIO} image in the "Bold Anime Reaction Thumbnail Style" visual style.

Subject: {SUBJECT}
Action: {SUBJECT_ACTION}
Prop/Product: {PRODUCT_OR_PROP}
Location: {LOCATION}
Background: {BACKGROUND_ELEMENTS}
Main text: {MAIN_TEXT}
Secondary text: {SECONDARY_TEXT}
Accent symbol: {ACCENT_SYMBOL}
Wardrobe/styling: {WARDROBE_STYLE}
Style fidelity anchors: {STYLE_FIDELITY_ANCHORS}
Source content to avoid: {SOURCE_CONTENT_TO_AVOID}

Apply these style rules:
- Build a dense anime web-thumbnail composition with oversized reaction characters on the outer edges and a smaller central discovery scene.
- Use clean glossy cel-shaded anime rendering, crisp black line art, smooth gradients, and bright commercial lighting.
- Put a huge uppercase yellow headline with thick black outline and hard drop shadow near the top.
- Use cool blue/cyan backgrounds, warm character colors, high-contrast black outlines, and a small yellow arrow or glow marker.
- Keep the scene fully clothed and non-sexual. Change the source subject, location, prop, action, text, and story premise.

Avoid:
- {NEGATIVE_PROMPT}

Important content rule: match the reference style first, then change the source content. Use new subjects, new scene details, new props or products, and new text, while preserving the style fidelity anchors.
